                            <comment id="17104481" author="davsclaus" created="Mon, 11 May 2020 14:04:53 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Ah thanks, can you try 3.4.0-SNAPSHOT just pushed some fixes&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17104492" author="jeremyross" created="Mon, 11 May 2020 14:19:33 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=davsclaus&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;davsclaus&quot;&gt;davsclaus&lt;/a&gt;&#160;I&apos;m not seeing 3.4.0-SNAPSHOT in the snapshot repo or git.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17104494" author="ancosen" created="Mon, 11 May 2020 14:21:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It&apos;s not moved to 3.4.0-SNAPSHOT, until we release 3.3.0 officialy&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17104504" author="jeremyross" created="Mon, 11 May 2020 14:34:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=davsclaus&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;davsclaus&quot;&gt;davsclaus&lt;/a&gt;&#160;I&apos;m building the salesforce component from master and, as of last night, I&apos;m still getting this exception.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17104511" author="davsclaus" created="Mon, 11 May 2020 14:42:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;You can also build from source locally&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17104517" author="jeremyross" created="Mon, 11 May 2020 14:47:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=davsclaus&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;davsclaus&quot;&gt;davsclaus&lt;/a&gt;&#160;I am building locally. That&apos;s what I meant when I said I&apos;m building the salesforce component from master (branch). Should this be sufficient to get the fix? Or do I need to build more than the salesforce component?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17104522" author="davsclaus" created="Mon, 11 May 2020 14:50:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I would built it all, or at least the core JARs also.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17105652" author="jeremyross" created="Tue, 12 May 2020 18:18:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=davsclaus&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;davsclaus&quot;&gt;davsclaus&lt;/a&gt;&#160;Fix looks good. Any chance this can make it in 3.3.0?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17105654" author="davsclaus" created="Tue, 12 May 2020 18:22:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for testing, now 3.3 is not a LTS release so not patches, wait for 3.4.0 to be released next month&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
